name: Peace Warning
description:
There are worlds around us that we never see. We go about our lives, necessarily unable to pay  close attention to everything. 
We choose, sending our energy in the form of seeing, focusing, observing and communicating. 

It's a signal from the world around you that goes unseen. 
Molecular
Atomic

You pass by, busy, occupied. 
Do your molecules and atoms attract a
signal as you pass by?

Look around you
What signal are you seeing?
What are you sending?
Blip.

in collaboration with Tom Blake
